Provides classes for all the pages available in the mobile app.

Package com.pom.crimson.pages Description

Provides classes for all the pages available in the mobile app.
These page classes contain MobileElements on the pages and functions to simulate interactions with these elements.
Author:
Sivaprakash.Selvaraj, Balaji.Sridharan, Jaspreet Kaur Chagger, Indirani.S
